#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.iloc.head:1 of
msgid "Return the first `n` rows."
msgstr "返回前 `n` 行。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.iloc.head:3 of
msgid ""
"This function returns the first `n` rows for the object based on "
"position. It is useful for quickly testing if your object has the right "
"type of data in it."
msgstr ""
"此函数根据位置返回对象的前 `n` 行。它可用于快速测试对象中是否包含正确类型"
"的数据。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.iloc.head:7 of
msgid ""
"For negative values of `n`, this function returns all rows except the "
"last `n` rows, equivalent to ``df[:-n]``."
msgstr "对于 `n` 的负值，此函数返回除最后 `n` 行之外的所有行，等价于 ``df[:-n]``。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.iloc.head of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.iloc.head:10 of
msgid "Number of rows to select."
msgstr "要选择的行数。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.iloc.head of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.iloc.head:13 of
msgid "The first `n` rows of the caller object."
msgstr "调用对象的前 `n` 行。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.iloc.head of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.iloc.head:18 of
msgid ":py:obj:`DataFrame.tail`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.iloc.head:19 of
msgid "Returns the last `n` rows."
msgstr "返回最后 `n` 行。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.iloc.head:22 of
msgid "示例"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.iloc.head:38 of
msgid "Viewing the first 5 lines"
msgstr "查看前 5 行"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.iloc.head:48 of
msgid "Viewing the first `n` lines (three in this case)"
msgstr "查看前 `n` 行（此例中为三行）"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.iloc.head:56 of
msgid "For negative values of `n`"
msgstr "对于 `n` 的负值"

